<br>
The Life of a Gnomish Wizard:<br>
<br>
I've learned the hard way that in your Class that TIMING isn't a big thing...IT'S THE ONLY THING!<br>
<br>
How &amp; WHEN you cast your spells is something new to me in a DD Spell Line. Cast Spell 1 which sets up the Mob for Spell 2. The Spell Lines here seem to have after effects similar to DOTs. And RANGE can make or break a pull.<br>
<br>
Is RANGE a Factor here in EQ? I ask because after the Kunark upgrade I noticed my spells had less range than before.<br>
<br>
I'm in Ardee hunting from the Hill beside the river. I am able to to hit &amp; pull Mods all the way across the beach &amp; it looks like a 1/2 mile. I have time to cast 4 more spells before I have to wack the Mob. Wish it was like that in here.<br>
<br>
Sill have Red Hair&amp; Still Short&amp;Still a Gnome,<br>
<br>
